title: FULL SHOW: We Chat With LaRussell, New Rihanna, Freaky Friday and More
itunes:title: FULL SHOW: We Chat With LaRussell, New Rihanna, Freaky Friday and More
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we have rapper and our friend LaRussell join us on the show and he even freestyles for us! Later on we talk about Rihanna's return to music on The Black Panther soundtrack. And lastly we ask our listeners about wet dreams
